  "rai:dataCollection": "HotpotQA-MaxionBench is deterministically derived from the official HotpotQA dev distractor source file. The preprocessing converts supporting-fact titles and contexts into paragraph-level retrieval qrels.",
  "rai:dataLimitation": "English Wikipedia-derived data, HotpotQA dev distractor only, paragraph-level evidence granularity, and local preprocessing assumptions. Conclusions should be limited to retrieval evidence coverage under the MaxionBench protocol.",
  "rai:dataPreprocessing": "The MaxionBench preprocessing script emits corpus.jsonl, queries.jsonl, qrels.tsv, manifest.json, meta.json, and checksums.json. The archived manifest records 66,635 documents, 7,405 questions, and 14,810 qrels.",
  "rai:dataUseCases": "Intended for retrieval-infrastructure evaluation and evidence-coverage auditing. Not intended for training or evaluating answer-generation quality.",
